---
title: Cincinnati Chili Spaghetti with Cheddar Cheese and Green Onions
description: You haven't lived until you've had Cincinnati chili! Developed by Macedonian immigrant restaurateurs, it's a diner classic of spiced meat sauce spooned over al dente spaghetti topped with cheddar cheese and green onions!
